trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de instâncias da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> especificado ao final do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index where the <paramref name="bindingOperationFault" /> parameter has been added.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero em que o parâmetro <paramref name="bindingOperationFault" /> foi adicionado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> for which to check collection membership.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> para o qual a associação da coleção é verificada.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> especificado é um membro do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="bindingOperationFault" /> parameter is a member of the <see langword="FaultBindingCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o parâmetro <paramref name="bindingOperationFault" /> for um membro do <see langword="FaultBindingCollection" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> especificado e retorna o índice de base zero da primeira ocorrência dentro de toda a coleção.

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer.
trans-unit.target: Um inteiro com sinal de 32 bits.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the <c>bindingOperationFault</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero no qual inserir o parâmetro <c>bindingOperationFault</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> to the <see langword="FaultBindingCollection" /> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBinding" /> especificado ao <see langword="FaultBindingCollection" /> no índice de base zero especificado.

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: Se o número de itens na coleção já for igual a capacidade da coleção, a capacidade é duplicada, automaticamente realocando a matriz interna antes do novo elemento é inserido.

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `bindingOperationFault` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Se o `index` parâmetro for igual ao <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, o `bindingOperationFault` parâmetro é adicionado ao final do <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.FaultBindingCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: Os elementos após o ponto de inserção se mover para baixo para acomodar o novo elemento.
